<h2>Who is Andrés Bronnimann?</h2>








  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            <img class="thumb-image" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5e50ac0a8bf5a551ea5e5f85/1607138154745-YSHTI83T4LBKXTABHO2J/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kO7fHNBA59ITqVO2FM7dTv97gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QHyNOqBUUEtDDsRWrJLTmkjk2jATZecDO8CG7f4FuaJ1xaLJmQuED3TSDsHdWAukNZf5Lhr2QEXLUKkQDIseJ/Untitled.png" data-image-dimensions="1257x1257" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="Untitled.png" data-load="false" data-image-id="5fcafb6a21c0486e918c6013" data-type="image" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5e50ac0a8bf5a551ea5e5f85/1607138154745-YSHTI83T4LBKXTABHO2J/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kO7fHNBA59ITqVO2FM7dTv97gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QHyNOqBUUEtDDsRWrJLTmkjk2jATZecDO8CG7f4FuaJ1xaLJmQuED3TSDsHdWAukNZf5Lhr2QEXLUKkQDIseJ/Untitled.png?format=1000w" />
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  


<p class="">Andrés Bronnimann was raised in Costa Rica, by a Swiss father and Mexican mother. He's a graduate of United World College Costa Rica and was a Davis Scholar at Ringling College of Art and Design, in Florida, USA, where he earned a degree in film and business.</p><p class="">Andrés' filmmaking portfolio is as diverse as his personal background, having worked for both social causes and large brands looking for an edgier media profile. His clients have ranged from Red Bull and Land Rover, to Projects for Peace. While pursuing freelance projects for other organizations, he also helped start an independent ad-agency, 'BE Latinoamérica', where he was CEO.</p><p class="">Throughout his film career, he has traveled to more than 30 countries, creating music videos, web series and commercials for numerous brands, artists and organizations. Andrés has worn many hats in the film production pipeline, having been a producer, writer, manager and creative. "The Universality of it All" is his debut film, nearly two years in the making, where he was the&nbsp;<em>only</em>&nbsp;crew member.</p>








  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
