<p class="sqsrte-large">Agustin Zavala on biotech, investing, starting a podcast and the creator’s journey</p><p class="">In Episode 2 of Learn With Avthar, I talk with biotech investor and good friend Agustin Zavala&nbsp;(@<a href="https://twitter.com/biotech_bros?lang=en">Biotech_Bros</a>). I learned a ton about biotech, investing and how to be a better creator from our conversation.</p><p class="">Ready to learn?</p><p class=""><strong>Listen on </strong><a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/2-biotech-bro-agustin-zavala-on-biotech-investing-starting/id1532246931?i=1000492652978"><strong>Apple Podcasts</strong></a></p><p class=""><strong>Listen on </strong><a href="https://open.spotify.com/episode/69xEl8wZC8Gc6FrI5yUxQO?si=KEO9y5gETh-XfSTwMzKLSA"><strong>Spotify</strong></a></p><p class=""><strong>Listen on </strong><a href="https://podcasts.google.com/feed/aHR0cHM6Ly9mZWVkcy5idXp6c3Byb3V0LmNvbS8xMjIwOTYzLnJzcw/episode/QnV6enNwcm91dC01NjEzOTQw?sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiWmoiJq43sAhXbhXIEHc2LBKMQkfYCegQIARAF"><strong>Google Podcasts</strong></a></p><p class="">Or listen <a href="https://avthar.buzzsprout.com/1220963/5613940-2-the-biotech-bro-agustin-zavala-on-biotech-investing-starting-a-podcast-the-creator-journey"><strong>online</strong></a><strong>:</strong></p><iframe allow="autoplay; fullscreen" scrolling="no" data-image-dimensions="500x210" allowfullscreen="true" src="//cdn.embedly.com/widgets/media.html?src=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzsprout.com%2F1220963%2F5613940-2-the-biotech-bro-agustin-zavala-on-biotech-investing-starting-a-podcast-the-creator-journey%3Fclient_source%3Dtwitter_card%26player_type%3Dfull_screen&amp;display_name=Buzzsprout&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Favthar.buzzsprout.com%2F1220963%2F5613940-2-the-biotech-bro-agustin-zavala-on-biotech-investing-starting-a-podcast-the-creator-journey&amp;image=https%3A%2F%2Favthar.buzzsprout.com%2Frails%2Factive_storage%2Frepresentations%2FeyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBCQ2YwU2dFPSIsImV4cCI6bnVsbCwicHVyIjoiYmxvY