%2Fwww.buzzsprout.com%2F1220963%2F5596795-how-to-find-business-ideas-make-something-you-want%3Fclient_source%3Dtwitter_card%26player_type%3Dfull_screen&amp;display_name=Buzzsprout&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Favthar.buzzsprout.com%2F1220963%2F5596795-how-to-find-business-ideas-make-something-you-want&amp;image=https%3A%2F%2Favthar.buzzsprout.com%2Frails%2Factive_storage%2Frepresentations%2FeyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBCQ2YwU2dFPSIsImV4cCI6bnVsbCwicHVyIjoiYmxvYl9pZCJ9fQ%3D%3D--3267a3ba6f8998c0966833aabf72c1e73f8adc92%2FeyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaDdCam9VWTI5dFltbHVaVjl2Y0hScGIyNXpld282QzNKbGMybDZaVWtpRFRJMU1IZ3lOVEJlQmpvR1JWUTZER2R5WVhacGRIbEpJZ3RqWlc1MFpYSUdPd2RVT2d0bGVIUmxiblJKSWd3eU5UQjRNalV3QmpzSFZEb01jWFZoYkdsMGVXbFZPZzlqYjJ4dmNuTndZV05sU1NJSmMxSkhRZ1k3QjFRPSIsImV4cCI6bnVsbCwicHVyIjoidmFyaWF0aW9uIn19--62c0dc9ae0106a9121f982eb952976ff55ebdee3%2FCopy%2520of%2520Learn%2520with%2520Avthar%2520Blue_%2520White.jpg&amp;key=61d05c9d54e8455ea7a9677c366be814&amp;type=text%2Fhtml&amp;schema=buzzsprout&amp;wmode=opaque" width="500" data-embed="true" frameborder="0" title="Buzzsprout embed" class="embedly-embed" height="210"></iframe><h2>Clip 4: The Creator's Journey: Biotech podcasting and investing</h2><p class="">Agustin Zavala (<a href="https://twitter.com/biotech_bros?lang=en">Biotech_Bros</a>) shares his journey to becoming a creator and entrepreneur.</p><p class="">Agustin gives us a behind the scenes look at what motivated him to start a podcast and investment fund focused on bio-tech investing. He shares how biotech investing and podcasting combined his natural interests and aligned his personality and natural strengths, leading him to start the Biotech Bros podcast.</p><p class="">Agustin also teaches us why biotech investing is different from investing in other kind of technology and tells us the story of his first investment and how it played out.</p><p class="">Article referenced:&nbsp;<a href="https://avthar.com/blog/strengths">How to Find Your Strengths: The Ultimate Guide</a></p><p class="">🎧 <a href="https://avthar.buzzsprout.com/1220963/5596744-the-creator-s-journey-biotech-podcasting-and-investing">Listen here</a></p><iframe allow="autoplay; fullscreen" scrolling="no" data-image-dimensions="500x210" allowfullscreen="true" src="//cdn.embedly.com/widgets/media.html?src=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzsprout.com%2F1220963%2F5596744-the-creator-s-journey-biotech-podcasting-and-investing%3Fclient_source%3Dtwitter_card%26player_type%3Dfull_screen&amp;display_name=Buzzsprout&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Favthar.buzzsprout.com%2F1220963%2F5596744-the-creator-s-journey-biotech-podcasting-and-investing&amp;image=https%3A%2F%2Favthar.buzzsprout.com%2Frails%2Factive_storage%2Frepresentations%2FeyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBCQ2YwU2dFPSIsImV4cCI6bnVsbCwicHVyIjoiYmxvYl9pZCJ9fQ%3D%3D--3267a3ba6f8998c0966833aabf72c1e73f8adc92%2FeyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaDdCam9VWTI5dFltbHVaVjl2Y0hScGIyNXpld282QzNKbGMybDZaVWtpRFRJMU1IZ3lOVEJlQmpvR1JWUTZER2R5WVhacGRIbEpJZ3RqWlc1MFpYSUdPd2RVT2d0bGVIUmxiblJKSWd3eU5UQjRNalV3QmpzSFZEb01jWFZoYkdsMGVXbFZPZzlqYjJ4dmNuTndZV05sU1NJSmMxSkhRZ1k3QjFRPSIsImV4cCI6bnVsbCwicHVyIjoidmFyaWF0aW9uIn19--62c0dc9ae0106a9121f982eb952976ff55ebdee3%2FCopy%2520of%2520Learn%2520with%2520Avthar%2520Blue_%2520White.jpg&amp;key=61d05c9d54e8455ea7a9677c366be814&amp;type=text%2Fhtml&amp;schema=buzzsprout&amp;wmode=opaque" width="500" data-embed="true" frameborder="0" title="Buzzsprout embed" class="embedly-embed" height="210"></iframe><h2><br>Clip 5: The Future of Content, Side Hustles and Monetization: Two creator's perspectives</h2><p class="">Agustin Zavala (<a href="https://twitter.com/biotech_bros?lang=en">Biotech_Bros</a>) and Avthar Sewrathan (@<a href="https://twitter.com/avthars">avthars</a>)discuss the future of their respective podcasts and content creation efforts. Why is creating content as on the side valuable? What opportunities could it lead to? How could it be monetized?</p><p class="">Along the way, they also discuss the importance of defining success for yourself, and the importance of an internal scorecard for your creative pursuits.</p><p class="">🎧 <a href="https://avthar.buzzsprout.com/1220963/5596768-the-future-of-content-side-hustles-and-monetization-two-creator-s-perspectives">Listen here</a></p><iframe allow="autoplay; fullscreen" scrolling="no" data-image-dimensions="500x210" allowfullscreen="true" src="//cdn.embedly.com/widgets/media.html?src=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzsprout.com%2F1220963%2F5596768-the-future-of-content-side-hustles-and-monetization-two-creator-s-perspectives%3Fclient_source%3Dtwitter_card%26player_type%3Dfull_screen&amp;display_name=Buzzsprout&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Favthar.buzzsprout.com%2F1220963%2F5596768-the-future-of-content-side-hustles-and-monetization-two-creator-s-perspectives&amp;image=https%3A%2F%2Favthar.buzzsprout.com%2Frails%2Factive_storage%2Frepresentations%2FeyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBCQ2YwU2dFPSIsImV4cCI6bnVsbCwicHVyIjoiYmxvYl9pZCJ9fQ%3D%3D--3267a3ba6f8998c0966833aabf72c1e73f8adc92%2FeyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaDdCam9VWTI5dFltbHVaVjl2Y0hScGIyNXpld282QzNKbGMybDZaVWtpRFRJMU1IZ3lOVEJlQmpvR1JWUTZER2R5WVhacGRIbEpJZ3RqWlc1MFpYSUdPd2RVT2d0bGVIUmxiblJKSWd3eU5UQjRNalV3QmpzSFZEb01jWFZoYkdsMGVXbFZPZzlqYjJ4dmNuTndZV05sU1NJSmMxSkhRZ1k3QjFRPSIsImV4cCI6bnVsbCwicHVyIjoidmFyaWF0aW9uIn19--62c0dc9ae0106a9121f982eb952976ff55ebdee3%2FCopy%2520of%2520Learn%2520with%2520Avthar%2520Blue_%2520White.jpg&amp;key=61d05c9d54e8455ea7a9677c366be814&amp;type=text%2Fhtml&amp;schema=buzzsprout&amp;wmode=opaque" width="500" data-embed="true" frameborder="0" title="Buzzsprout embed" class="embedly-embed" height="210"></iframe><h2>Subscribe and Share!</h2><p class="">Do subscribe to both the <a href="https://avthar.buzzsprout.com/1220963">podcast</a> and my <a href="https://avthar.substack.com">newsletter</a> below to ensure you are the first to know about new episodes! </p><p class="">If you’ve learned something from the episode, please do share it with friends, 