            <img class="thumb-image" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5e50ac0a8bf5a551ea5e5f85/1595561342887-07SQPJ6DVTUBCJBZSZJI/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kD33KhhWEodMJvcytjXFyvFZw-zPPgdn4jUwVcJE1ZvWQUxwkmyExglNqGp0IvTJZamWLI2zvYWH8K3-s_4yszcp2ryTI0HqTOaaUohrI8PIQVUjsvMYGrjk5P5guv3Gb1aPQrnDLhtGUJ-UJkarKCw/RBS+Starter+Kit.png" data-image-dimensions="960x540" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="RBS Starter Kit.png" data-load="false" data-image-id="5f1a557e5c8f396c5b4c985e" data-type="image" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5e50ac0a8bf5a551ea5e5f85/1595561342887-07SQPJ6DVTUBCJBZSZJI/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kD33KhhWEodMJvcytjXFyvFZw-zPPgdn4jUwVcJE1ZvWQUxwkmyExglNqGp0IvTJZamWLI2zvYWH8K3-s_4yszcp2ryTI0HqTOaaUohrI8PIQVUjsvMYGrjk5P5guv3Gb1aPQrnDLhtGUJ-UJkarKCw/RBS+Starter+Kit.png?format=1000w" />
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  


<p class="">If you’re looking to deepen your self-awareness, want to understand how you can make the best impact or just looking to be world class at what you do, the <a href="https://avthar.substack.com/p/how-to-find-your-strengths-part-2"><span>Reflected Best Self</span></a> (RBS) will take you to the next level.</p><h2>Wait what is an RBS?</h2><p class="">The RBS will help you examine the impact you’ve made on people in different parts of your life and nudge you to redesign your life around your strengths, so that you can maximize impact and personal fulfillment.&nbsp;</p><p class="">I’ve written a step-by-step guide on how to find Your Reflected Best Self.</p><ol data-rte-list="default"><li><p class=""><a href="https://avthar.substack.com/p/how-to-find-your-strengths-part-2"><span>List 10+ people from different parts of your life</span></a></p></li><li><p class=""><a href="https://avthar.substack.com/p/how-to-find-your-strengths-part-2"><span>Ask them, “When was I at my best?” and collect their responses</span></a></p></li><li><p class="">Look for patterns in the responses</p></li><li><p class="">Compose your self portrait of who you are at your best</p></li><li><p class="">Redesign your life around your strengths</p></li></ol><p class="">Steps 1-2 are <a href="https://avthar.substack.com/p/how-to-find-your-strengths-part-2">Part 1</a> of the guide. Steps 3-5 are in Part 2.</p><p class="">Now that you’ve seen all 5 steps of the Reflected Best Self Exercise, it’s your turn to try it and unlock a deeper understanding of your strengths and who you are at your best!</p><h2>The RBS Starter Kit</h2><p class="">To help you get started, I’ve put together an RBS Starter Kit to kickstart your journey.</p><p class="">The starter kit contains scripts, templates and sample artifacts which I’ve developed for myself when doing my yearly RBS. I’m super excited to share them with you and hope they help you overcome the initial hurdle of resistance.</p><p class=""><strong>For Step 2:</strong></p><h3>📝<a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1nk7mXku5ejIj5KOTPs94hJHnA2x8UK-2coYn3jK6Wl4/edit?usp=sharing"><span><strong>Template Google Form</strong></span></a>&nbsp;</h3><p class="">Here’s a <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1nk7mXku5ejIj5KOTPs94hJHnA2x8UK-2coYn3jK6Wl4/edit?usp=sharing">template form</a> which you can copy and modify to use as your survey form.Do change the heading to include your name and modify the form description to your taste. Just Add a copy of this template to your google drive, change your name and you’re off to the races!</p>








  

    
  
    

      

      
