<h3>📲Message Scripts</h3><p class="">Here’s the exact script I used to reach out to people in order to ask them to respond to the survey. You can use this verbatim or as the basis for your outreach message. I usually reached out to people in the place I talked with them, so Slack and email for co-workers, and text / Whatsapp/ Facebook for friends and family.</p><p class=""><strong>For colleagues/ boss / professional contexts:</strong><br></p>








  

    
  
    

      

      
